GONNA LET YOUR WIFE

36:01.642 --> 36:05.646
TAKE THE FALL FOR SOMETHING
YOU DID, ARE YOU, THOMAS?

36:05.680 --> 36:08.925
THOMAS,
DON'T SAY ANYTHING.

36:12.963 --> 36:14.827
NO.

36:14.862 --> 36:15.897
NO, HE'S RIGHT.

36:15.932 --> 36:16.967
DON'T...

36:18.831 --> 36:20.626
HE'S RIGHT.

36:20.661 --> 36:22.663
I'VE BEEN CARRYING THIS AROUND
FAR TOO LONG.

36:30.671 --> 36:34.709
WHEN MICHELLE AND I FIRST
STARTED SEEING DR. CORVIS,

36:34.744 --> 36:36.746
THE TREATMENT WAS WORKING.

36:36.780 --> 36:37.919
I WOULD TAKE THE DRUG,

36:37.954 --> 36:40.646
AND IT WOULD MAKE ME FEEL THINGS
FOR MY WIFE.

36:40.681 --> 36:43.925
BUT AS THE SESSIONS CONTINUED,

36:43.960 --> 36:45.893
I STARTED HAVING FEELINGS
FOR JULIAN.

36:45.927 --> 36:48.861
SO HE CALLED ME,

36:48.896 --> 36:51.623
AND HE ASKED ME TO COME IN
FOR A PRIVATE SESSION.

36:51.657 --> 36:54.660
WE STARTED
TALKING ABOUT MY PROBLEM,

36:54.695 --> 36:56.697
BUT WE COULDN'T HELP
OURSELVES.

37:01.909 --> 37:04.049
BUT I HATED MYSELF.

37:05.775 --> 37:09.744
MICHELLE AND I WENT TO JULIAN
SO THAT I COULD BE WITH HER,

37:09.779 --> 37:10.952
BECAUSE I LOVE HER.

37:12.920 --> 37:16.820
WHAT WE WERE DOING WAS WRONG.

37:16.855 --> 37:18.684
SO I WENT BACK TO HIS OFFICE

37:18.719 --> 37:21.963
TO GET THE PILLS SO I COULD USE
THEM WITH MY WIFE.

37:23.724 --> 37:27.659
WHAT YOU AND I ARE, WHAT
WE WANT, IT'S NOT A DISEASE.

37:27.693 --> 37:28.901
I REALIZE THAT NOW.

37:28.936 --> 37:31.904
I-I'VE BEEN TRYING TO CONVINCE
MY PATIENTS, CONVINCE MYSELF!

37:31.939 --> 37:33.734
BUT I'VE BEEN LIVING
A LIE.

37:33.768 --> 37:36.633
I SEE THAT NNO.

37:36.668 --> 37:37.669
WE CAN BE TOGETHER.

37:37.703 --> 37:39.671
I WANT TO BE
WITH MY WIFE!

37:39.705 --> 37:42.674
BUT...

37:42.708 --> 37:44.710
[ Voice breaking ]
...I LOVE YOU.

37:51.890 --> 37:54.789
AND I'M SORRY.

37:59.691 --> 38:02.797
I AM SOSORRY.

38:06.732 --> 38:07.940
Natalie: IT'S TRAGIC.

38:07.975 --> 38:09.942
THREE PEOPLE'S LIVES
DESTROYED

38:09.977 --> 38:12.945
BECAUSE THEY COULDN'T ACCEPT
WHO THEY REALLY WERE.

38:12.980 --> 38:15.983
THE NOTION THAT SOME MAGIC PILL
COULD TAKE AWAY ALL THAT PAIN?

38:16.017 --> 38:18.744
IT MUST HAVE BEEN
PRETTY TEMPTING.

38:18.779 --> 38:19.849
THERE ARE PILLS
YOUCAN TAKE, DANIEL.

38:19.883 --> 38:20.919
YOU KNOW THAT.

38:20.953 --> 38:22.955
AIN'T NO PILL
GONNA CURE MY ILL.

38:22.990 --> 38:25.751
IT WOULD PROBABLY HELP
WITH YOUR SYMPTOMS.

38:25.786 --> 38:28.823
MAYBE MY SYMPTOMS
MAKE ME WHO I AM.

38:28.858 --> 38:29.893
THAT'S A COP-OUT.

38:29.928 --> 38:31.964
YOU KNOW YOU SHOULD BE
ON MEDS.

38:31.999 --> 38:35.692
LET'S GO, DOC.
YOU'RE LATE.

38:35.727 --> 38:37.694
[ GROANS ]

38:38.868 --> 38:40.663
YOU THINK I SHOULD GO?

38:40.697 --> 38:42.768
STOP AVOIDING
THIS CONVERSATION.

38:42.803 --> 38:45.978
OKAY, EITHER YOU PUT IT ON,
OR I STUFF YOU IN IT.

38:49.016 --> 38:50.949
YOU HEARD THE MAN.

38:54.884 --> 38:57.024
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

39:10.865 --> 39:13.834
DANIEL!

39:13.868 --> 39:14.973
[ Sighing ]
OH, KATE.

39:15.007 --> 39:16.871
PLEASE TELL ME
YOU'VE GOT ANOTHER CASE

39:16.906 --> 39:18.735
AND YOU'RE GETTING ME
THE [BLEEP] OUT OF HERE.

39:18.770 --> 39:21.669
SO, SORRY. [ CHUCKLES ]
I WOULHI, DANIEL.

39:21.704 --> 39:24.016
I HAD SOME TROUBLE FINDING
A PARKING SPOT. ALLOW ME.

39:27.986 --> 39:29.746
YOU LOOK BEAUTIFUL.

39:29.781 --> 39:30.989
WELL, THANK YOU.

39:32.749 --> 39:35.787
YOU CLEAN UP
PRETTY WELL YOURSELF.

39:35.821 --> 39:37.858
AH.

39:37.892 --> 39:39.722
WE WERE GONNA GO GRAB A DRINK.
CARE TO JORIGHT.

39:39.756 --> 39:43.070
NO, I-I THINK I AM
GALA'D OUT TONIGHT.

39:43.104 --> 39:46.798
[ Chuckling ] RIGHT,
WELL, SOME OTHER TIME THEN.

39:48.731 --> 39:50.077
Kate:
SEE YOU, DANIEL.

39:50.111 --> 39:53.874
DANIEL. THERE YOU ARE.
NO, OH...

39:53.908 --> 39:54.944
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
COME ON!

39:54.978 --> 39:55.979
PLEASE,
DON'T MAKE ME.

39:56.014 --> 39:57.809
SHE'S A BIG FAN!
NO, NO, NO.

39:57.843 --> 40:03.090
I JUST WANT TO INTRODUCE YOU
TO ALLISON BANNISTER.

40:06.921 --> 40:09.786
WOW.
YOU ARE NOT OLD.

40:09.821 --> 40:11.995
[ LAUGHS ]

40:12.030 --> 40:14.929
WELL, YOU ARE QUITE
THE OBSERVATIONAL SCIENTIST.

40:14.964 --> 40:16.759
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

40:16.793 --> 40:19.762
MRS. BANNISTER, I'M TOLD
THAT I CAN BE, UH, OVERLY BLUNT,

40:19.796 --> 40:22.005
SO FORGIVE ME IN ADVANCE
WHEN I SAY

40:22.040 --> 40:23.869
THAT I AM
ONLY HERE TONIGHT

40:23.904 --> 40:25.940
BECAUSE I'M INTERESTED
I-IN PROCURING SEX.

40:25.975 --> 40:30.876
I MEAN,
MONEY...FOR A DONATION.

40:30.911 --> 40:33.707
WHO KNOWS?

40:33.741 --> 40:36.019
IF YOU PLAY YOUR CARDS RIGHT,
DR. PIERCE,

40:36.054 --> 40:39.057
YOU MIGHT JUST GET BOTH.

40:43.751 --> 40:45.028
WOW.

40:45.063 --> 40:47.962
NICE WORK, HMM?

40:49.757 --> 40:52.001
Daniel: IS THERE SOMETHING WRONG
WITH ME?

40:52.035 --> 40:54.693
IT'S A QUESTION
WE ALL ASK OURSELVES.

40:54.728 --> 40:58.697
WE ALL WONDER WHY WE DON'T
LOOK LIKE, ACT LIKE,

40:58.732 --> 41:00.734
FEEL LIKE EVERYBODY ELSE.

41:00.768 --> 41:04.876
EACH OF OUR BRAINS
HAS THE EXACT SAME PARTS --

41:04.910 --> 41:07.879
CORTEX, HYPOTHALAMUS, FORNIX,
SEPTAL NUCLEUS, SO ON.

41:07.913 --> 41:13.712
AND YET, NO TWO BRAINS
ARE EXACTLY ALIKE.

41:13.747 --> 41:17.923
SO, BEING DIFFERENT...

41:22.928 --> 41:24.930
...BEING UNIQUE...

41:26.760 --> 41:30.971
...IS UNDENIABLY
A FUNDAMENTAL CHARACTERISTIC...

41:33.767 --> 41:35.976
...OF BEING HUMAN.
